{
  "stem": "27285.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because later on, again, you find some kind-- you find a way to cope with it, or it becomes in a form a routine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But these first days, which is like-- hell has no-- really has no-- there is no image of the [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dante ?] anybody, or I don't know if there's-- hell exists in our religion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I hope not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That it could be possible what could be done to you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in a state of [INAUDIBLE] you-- you get numb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't even know that you are cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, you are nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You are just nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So slowly you get to recognize your Laura or whoever person you have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was, of course, no child anymore around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was only by sheer chance that I was still-- I mean, I was already almost three years in Terezin, so I was not such a very healthy and good looking girl.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The orderly told us, you have to say you are either 18 or not more than 35 and not less than 18 or something, because otherwise you will not survive.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said, oh, this is just the propaganda.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are so long here, they don't know what they're talking about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- you could not grasp that it is possible I mean--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they were murdering people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they are murdering people on such a scale, and that they are-- what do you mean gas?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, who knows about gas?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, who would comprehend such a thing?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's very hard to say today, because today everybody knows.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
